{"tid":2219642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發現老公係我大肚其間玩女人","createTime":"2020-09-27T04:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T12:34:46.000Z","uid":1734,"like":9,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"919f7fee2ca96103ea9ea245ea121c8c006de63b","tid":2219642,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"同我老公一齊左十幾年，結左婚幾年，最近無意中發現老公係我大肚其間同朋友去旅行個陣玩女人！<br />\n<br />\n我問過佢幾次都唔認，仲發返我脾氣，話我無野搵野講，仲話係咪要逼到大家離婚先安落！<br />\n<br />\n我一直都好相信佢唔會去搞三搞四，但我係佢電話搵到證明，我俾左好幾次機會都自己解釋，佢係一個大話遮一個大話，仲係堅持唔認！<br />\n<br />\n係我逼問下，其實係我將啲證據攞晒出黎，佢再搵唔到籍口之下佢承認左，但佢話只係同一齊訓過，無搞到！<br />\n<br />\n我辛辛苦苦同佢生左2個，點解咁對我，呢2日不停喊，佢仲問返我轉頭係咪有必要要離婚！我俾晒機會佢，佢仍然係講大話！<br />\n<br />\n心好痛，我應該點做？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baa0036e2152af93d48a23655f3b115eceeeea3","tid":2219642,"uid":283207,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"Sis有冇諗過出軌報復佢？"},{"pid":"a9b6eb101c89517d2ff46557a7c3e3ccc052cf0b","tid":2219642,"uid":152340,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"死gay佬"},{"pid":"5af4434f607b9729df6e9f91564c65f817992868","tid":2219642,"uid":60109,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"感情問題一律...."},{"pid":"e1af3df8e9d33be9d54e4ac15f412cc6739bf81f","tid":2219642,"uid":10165,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"你個啤酒肚黎"},{"pid":"7d492b7fadee5cd7bb486910c8b9c91bb4da1925","tid":2219642,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4baa0036e2152af93d48a23655f3b115eceeeea3","tid":2219642,"uid":283207,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"Sis有冇諗過出軌報復佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"心好亂"},{"pid":"c225cbeb4845437ef8551564a16bcab6ae41ddf5","tid":2219642,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:42:50.000